column3: Stream Catchment code where the pCO2 estimates exists. The code is derived from the EPA StreamCat dataset within the NHDPlus dataset.
US state where data point was located, given in standard state abbreviation code
pH given in standard pH units
total alkalinity in units - micro equivilence per kilogram water
partial pressure of CO2 given in units - micro atmospheres
CO2 concentrations given in units - milligrams per liter
